At Advent Auto, we specialize in Complete Auto Repair of all makes of domestic and foreign vehicles with 100% guaranteed service by our ASE certified, factory trained technicians. The auto experts at Advent Auto have over 50 years of combined mechanical experience and use only state of the art equipment. You want to get the most from your car and you don't want problems -- That's why preventative maintenance and quality repair are important considerations. With that in mind, why not take advantage of our experience to keep your vehicle running efficiently for years to come? We care about our customers. Each vehicle is added to our database to maintain records of repair and maintenance history. As a AAA Approved Auto Repair facility, both of our locations are inspected and tested every year to make sure that we meet AAAs highest standard for service. Not only are we judged by the AAA for the services we provide, but also by our local reputation, appearance, staff qualifications and equipment.
